<aura:documentation>
	<aura:description>
        <p>Component that allows for the search of addresses typed on the input. Search is a callout to Informatica webservice with defined parameters on the APEX controller </p>
        <p>Input is a pure SLDS combobox, placing and other styling must be done externally</p>
        <p>This component must receive a country ISO code (2-char) to be used on the search</p>
        <p>Component sends the OneId_AddressSelected_EVT event with an object containing the selected result</p>
        
